# Project overview

Personal landing for a **Fullstack Developer** (6 years commercial experience, frontend-first positioning without explicit grade).

## Audience

- HR and recruiters
- CTOs and engineering managers
- CEOs and founders
- International remote-first companies

## Product goals

- Showcase dashboard/SaaS frontend expertise via **preview case cards** on home and **full case studies** on `/cases/:slug`
- Present separate homepage blocks for **management skills**, **AI skills**, and **measurable achievements**
- Communicate stack: TypeScript, Vue/Nuxt, React/Next.js, FSD, monorepos, real-time, design systems
- Signal **English B2** and remote readiness

## Visual system

- Premium dark-tech + clean light mode
- Editorial layout, modern SaaS feel
- Dark background, soft gradients, thin borders, glass cards, strong typography
- Minimal animation (fade-up, card hover, slow gradient drift)
- Avoid cyberpunk, aggressive neon, heavy 3D
